Step 2:
 $f_{p+1}(N)=\sum_{i=0}h_p(\lfloor\frac{N}{p^i}\rfloor)=h_p(N)+f_{p+1}(\lfloor\frac{N}{p}\rfloor)$
These could solve in $O\left(\frac{\sqrt N \times \sqrt B}{\log n}\right)$.

